name: iC³ Life Science and Healthcare Innovation Summit 2025
description: iC³ Life Science and Healthcare Innovation Summit is an event hosted for professionals focused on Medical & Pharma. The event brings together leaders, innovators, and visionaries from the life sciences and healthcare sectors to foster collaboration and drive advancements in the industry, allowing attendees to have the opportunity to engage in thought-provoking discussions, attend insightful panels, and network with key stakeholders.

name: Doctoral Defense of J.C. Esteves Martins 2025
description: Doctoral Defense of J.C. Esteves Martins 2025 is an event hosted for academic scholars, research supervisors, graduate students, and subject matter experts focused on evaluating and celebrating original contributions to the field of study presented by doctoral candidate J.C. Esteves Martins. The event brings together industry professionals to connect on topics of focus related to the candidate’s dissertation, allowing attendees to engage in scholarly dialogue, assess the rigor and relevance of the research, and support the advancement of academic excellence.

name: Neuroscience of the Everyday World Conference 2025
description: Neuroscience of the Everyday World Conference 2025 is an event hosted for cognitive scientists, neuroscientists, and applied technology researchers. The event brings together industry professionals to connect on real-world applications of neuroscience, allowing attendees to explore how tools like fNIRS and EEG can be used to study cognition in naturalistic settings and advance understanding of brain function in everyday environments.
attendeeNamesConcatString: ANT Neuro, Artinis Medical Systems, Edmund Optics, Gowerlabs, Kernel (Monitoring Equipment), NIRx Medical Technologies, OptiTrack, iMotions
